{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":6},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5},"Sicile","","1896","\u003Cspan>Paolo Orsi, « Sicile », \u003Ci>Bulletin de Correspondance Hellénique\u003C/i> 20 (1896): 399‑400\u003C/span>",[7,108,162,235,287,339],{"file":8,"uri":8,"title":9,"status":10,"editionAuthor":12,"type":13,"objectType":17,"material":21,"condition":3,"layoutDesc":25,"handNote":32,"date":46,"places":51,"geo":60,"provenance":53,"provenanceGeo":64,"country":67,"region":68,"settlement":69,"repository":70,"idno":74,"textLang":77,"tmNumber":3,"letterHeights":81,"publications":82,"zotero":86,"keywords":90,"html":101,"bibl":102},"ISic001869","Funerary inscription for Artemo",{"_":11},"edited",null,{"_":14,"ana":15,"ref":16},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":18,"ana":19,"ref":20},"block","#object.block","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html",{"_":22,"ana":23,"ref":24},"limestone","#material.stone.limestone","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html",{"layout":26},{"p":27,"rs":28,"damage":3},"Three lines of Greek letters, seemingly not centered / regularly laid out.",{"_":29,"ana":30,"ref":31},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":33,"dimensions":34},"Described by Orsi (1896) as 'scritto a pessimi caratteri', and (1899) as 'lettere cattive, rustiche cosi che a tutta prima sembrano archaiche, e molto sconservate... L'iscrizione negligentemente redatta e scolpita è funebre di tarda età'. Pace states 'lettere del III sec. av. Cr.', but given the presence of lunate epsilon and Orsi's comments, a later date seems much more likely.",[35,42],{"type":36,"l":37,"from":38,"to":39,"h":40,"unit":41},"letterHeight","Line 1-3","line1","line3","55-95","mm",{"type":43,"l":44,"from":38,"to":45,"unit":41},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","line2",{"_":47,"notBefore":48,"notAfter":49,"evidence":50},"Suggested to be of later Roman date by Orsi on the basis of lettering etc.",101,400,"lettering",[52,56],{"_":53,"type":54,"ref":55},"Kamarina","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462126",{"_":57,"type":58,"ref":59},"Santa Croce Camerina","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6540853",[61],[62,63],36.8736,14.4507,[65,66],36.8759983,14.4377781,"Italy","Sicily","Siracusa",{"_":71,"role":72,"ref":73},"Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/097",{"_":75,"type":76},"16474","inventory",{"_":78,"mainLang":79,"languages":80},"Ancient Greek","grc",[78],[],[83,84,85],"Sicile, 1896","Camarina (Campagna archeologica del 1896), 1899","Camarina: topografia, storia, archeologia, 1927",[87,88,89],"FWX5CWBN","ICW2M9P2","ZJ6KUFMM",[91,92,93,14,18,22,94,95,96,97,98,99,100,79],"isic001869","funerary inscription for artemo",{"_":11},"kamarina","santa croce camerina","italy","sicily","siracusa","museo archeologico regionale paolo orsi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμοι\n                    Ἀρτεμιδό\n                    του\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμοι\">Ἀρτεμοι̣\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμιδό\n                    του\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμιδό\n                    του\">Ἀρτεμιδό \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>τ̣ου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"χαῖρε\">χαῖρε\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\